<p class="entry-meta"><time class="entry-time" itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2016-05-15T22:10:54+00:00">May 15, 2016</time> by <span class="entry-author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="http://www.chakranews.com/author/romika/" class="entry-author-link" itemprop="url" rel="author"><span class="entry-author-name" itemprop="name">Editor</span></a></span>  </p></header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><div id="attachment_5493" style="width: 750px" class="wp-caption alignleft"><img class="size-full wp-image-5493" src="http://www.chakranews.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/The-Vedas-are-Vedic-Hindu-Scriptures-and-Among-the-Oldest-Living-Texts-in-the-World.jpg" alt="The Vedas are Vedic Hindu Scriptures and Among the Oldest Living Texts in the World" width="740" srcset="http://www.chakranews.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/The-Vedas-are-Vedic-Hindu-Scriptures-and-Among-the-Oldest-Living-Texts-in-the-World.jpg 600w, http://www.chakranews.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/The-Vedas-are-Vedic-Hindu-Scriptures-and-Among-the-Oldest-Living-Texts-in-the-World-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /><p class="wp-caption-text">The Vedas are Vedic Hindu Scriptures and Among the Oldest Living Texts in the World</p></div>
<p>Dr. S. Srinivas</p><!--Ad Injection:top-->
