			<p>The author of this article seems to have lost sight of the point that Vedas are apauru?eya which means they were not composed by *anyone*, not even Bhagav?n Himself. </p>
<p>The ??is are not the composers of the mantras. The mantras are eternal. That is an axiom of Ved?ntic thought.</p>
